textContent:
---dump---

The following are like several thoughts I had for the past week but like, di ko lang nasulat agad kase busy akong dinadaldal/linalandi ka HAHAHAHAHAHA MWAAA I LOVE YOU

---i love you more---

I've told you about this a while ago actually, habang nasa kama mo tayo (HWJWKSKKSKAKA YIIEEEE HEHHEHE MWAAA RAWWRRR). It's about when you got mad kase I joked about how I love you much much more hahaha. 

I told you na for me, me loving you more is something that I can actually be proud of. I've said this very early on in our relationship, but I really like the way I am when I'm loving you, Rei. Loving you feels good. Loving you feels right. Loving you feels like destiny and fate. And thus, I really like loving you. I'll love you more. Sabi nga nung sinend mong tiktok, I'll never finish loving you. Lulunurin kita sa pag-ibig ko. And I'm proud and thankful, that I get to love you. That I get to experience for someone as beautiful, as sweet, as kind, as thoughtful and smart, as someone like you.

Don't get me wrong though, kinilig ako nung sinabi mo na ayaw mong mas mahal kita hahahaha. Na competitive ka rin. Na gusto mo mahal na mahal na mahal na mahal mo rin ako. AND I FEEL IT!!! I always feel your love, your care, and your affection. I won't be like this if I didn't. There has never been a moment in our relationship wherein I felt unsure of your feelings for me. I've always felt them. But guess what? Competitive talaga ako so bleh. Hihigatan ko lang lalo yung nararamdaman mo para sakin. Mwa. Didiw.

---rei-sickness---

Ang tagal nating di nagkita this week!!!! (3 days lang, ang OA ko talaga HAHAHAHA deal with it). I've missed you a lot this week Rei!!! Jusko ang hirap mangulila sayo. Para talaga akong nababaliw pag di kita kasama. Ang daming beses kong naiisip na sana kasama kita. Ang daming beses kong napapatingin sa phone ko tas titignan ko lang pics naten tas mamimiss lang kita lalo huhu. 

Kahit na magka-call tayo halos everyday, na mimiss parin kita lalo. Iba talaga yung dating ng physical presence mo. Gusto kitang yinayakap. Gusto kitang hinahalikan. Gusto kitang nakikita. Gusto kong hinahawakan kamay mo. Grabe. Mukhang lalala nalang talaga lalo to Rei. 

Kaya nung nakita kita kanina talaga, I couldn't contain the excitement. I couldn't contain all of the pent up energy that I had for you. Sorry kung tingin mo nasisiraan nako ng bait non. Mahal na mahal lang talaga kita at miss na miss lang talaga kita kaya ganon huhuhu. I like having fun with you. I like teasing you. I can't wait for the day where we spend everyday together.

---cuddles---

Reilapse lang malala don sa kanina nung nakauwi na parents mo tas nag cucuddle lang tayo sa bed mo. Wala lang huhuhu. Ang wholesome. Sobrang cute mo rin nung ayaw mo ko pauwiin HUHUHU My baby is so adorable!!!!! I love you so much!!! Ganon rin nafefeel ko lagi bby huhuhu. I don't want my time with you to end kase I enjoy them so much pero they all just seem to fly so fast. I miss you already cutie. Matutulog na nga ako, kikitain pa kita bukas mwaaa hehe. I hope you're already sleeping tight na.
